<emphasis id="A39FEACDFFB2BA1EB49CF1F8B16DF977" bold="true" box="[142,843,1688,1721]" pageId="14" pageNumber="633">Movements, Home range and Social organization.</emphasis>
No information.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="D9F16554FFB2BA1EB49DF1DFB68FF92E" box="[143,1193,1727,1760]" pageId="14" pageNumber="633" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="915436DFFFB2BA1EB49DF1DFB68FF92E" blockId="14.[141,1349,1179,1842]" box="[143,1193,1727,1760]" pageId="14" pageNumber="633">
<emphasis id="A39FEACDFFB2BA1EB49DF1DFB3CAF92E" bold="true" box="[143,492,1727,1760]" pageId="14" pageNumber="633">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
